00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:03.680
Like I feel like in everything
you have like a soul mate.

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:04.510
Right?

00:17:04.510 --> 00:17:08.660
If I had to just give like one
line about the city of Detroit,

00:17:08.660 --> 00:17:11.490
I would most definitely
say that I belong here.

00:17:11.490 --> 00:17:13.540
And it is definitely
a soul mate of mine.

00:17:13.540 --> 00:17:15.380
I was working on this
poem a few days ago.

00:17:15.380 --> 00:17:17.050
It's about the city of Detroit.

00:17:17.050 --> 00:17:21.506
But it's how it breathes
like, greatness, great kids,

00:17:21.506 --> 00:17:23.130
great boys, great
girls, how we grow up

00:17:23.130 --> 00:17:24.380
to be great men and women.

00:17:24.380 --> 00:17:27.079
And I wanted to read it
to you, if that's fine.

00:17:27.079 --> 00:17:30.750
"Somewhere in the
projects, there's

00:17:30.750 --> 00:17:34.750
a kid working on a project
to project to the world.

00:17:34.750 --> 00:17:38.100
He lives in a city that grows
boys and girls into lions

00:17:38.100 --> 00:17:41.220
and tigers, a city that
takes the fire and the ashes,

00:17:41.220 --> 00:17:44.120
builds, rebuilds,
turns abandoned houses

00:17:44.120 --> 00:17:46.480
and empty fields into
things worth looking at.

00:17:46.480 --> 00:17:48.210
A place that never looks back.

00:17:48.210 --> 00:17:51.230
The center stage of a nation,
the heartbeat, the patience,

00:17:51.230 --> 00:17:54.470
the music, the Motown, the
midtown, the downtown, the

00:17:54.470 --> 00:17:55.790
always come back around.

00:17:55.790 --> 00:17:58.110
We fight for our
reputation, walk, ride,

00:17:58.110 --> 00:17:59.450
bike to our destination.

00:17:59.450 --> 00:18:02.640
Practice patient knows that
they can't forget about us.

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:05.680
Detroit, the city that continues
to call the world's bluff.

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:09.060
Somewhere there's a kid
working on a project

00:18:09.060 --> 00:18:13.210
to project from a city that's
rebuilding, that we building

00:18:13.210 --> 00:18:17.500
from the ashes together
so that everywhere there

00:18:17.500 --> 00:18:18.790
can be Detroit.

00:18:20.250 --> 00:18:20.890
-Beautiful.

00:18:20.890 --> 00:18:21.330
God bless you.

00:18:21.330 --> 00:18:21.830
-Thank you.

00:18:21.830 --> 00:18:22.580
Thank you.

00:18:22.580 --> 00:18:23.710
-God bless you.

00:18:23.710 --> 00:18:25.360
-I'm glad you liked it.

00:18:25.360 --> 00:18:28.407
Thank you.

