00:48:02.080 --> 00:48:05.580
So what are the global
brands, the iconic brands

00:48:05.580 --> 00:48:08.400
that may be on the wall or
in the thoughts of those

00:48:08.400 --> 00:48:10.444
at Shinola to emulate?

00:48:10.444 --> 00:48:12.860
BRIDGET RUSSO: You know, even
though we poked fun at them,

00:48:12.860 --> 00:48:16.320
Apple definitely is up there.

00:48:16.320 --> 00:48:18.950
And it was all in good fun.

00:48:18.950 --> 00:48:21.150
You know, Tesla.

00:48:21.150 --> 00:48:22.690
Virgin.

00:48:22.690 --> 00:48:25.340
These are all brands
that we aspire to.

00:48:25.340 --> 00:48:29.630
I think Tesla would probably
be number one on that list.

00:48:29.630 --> 00:48:30.140
You know.

00:48:30.140 --> 00:48:35.040
And it's been amazing to
just be a part of what's

00:48:35.040 --> 00:48:35.950
happening in Detroit.

00:48:35.950 --> 00:48:38.580
We're one of you guys know,
how many people they're

00:48:38.580 --> 00:48:42.090
working both small and on a
large scale like Dan Gilbert

00:48:42.090 --> 00:48:44.590
to really help bring the
city back on its feet.

00:48:44.590 --> 00:48:46.760
And my hope is that
it continues to be

00:48:46.760 --> 00:48:50.590
a place of equal opportunity,
that it doesn't just

00:48:50.590 --> 00:48:57.610
become my lovely New York,
that million dollar plus condos

00:48:57.610 --> 00:49:01.030
that most people can't
afford, because it really

00:49:01.030 --> 00:49:04.540
hurts a city when it becomes
homogeneous like that.

00:49:04.540 --> 00:49:08.730
So you have to make sure there's
a balance of opportunity that

00:49:08.730 --> 00:49:10.900
maintains the diversity.

00:49:10.900 --> 00:49:15.100
That's one thing that I think
New York lost over the years,

00:49:15.100 --> 00:49:17.600
because now you turn around,
and everywhere you go-- I mean,

00:49:17.600 --> 00:49:20.130
Bed-Stuy, which I
remember growing up

00:49:20.130 --> 00:49:22.260
as a kid in Brooklyn,
you just didn't go there.

00:49:22.260 --> 00:49:25.570
And now it's like luxury
apartment buildings

00:49:25.570 --> 00:49:29.220
and townhouses all
over the place.

00:49:29.220 --> 00:49:29.720
So.

00:49:29.720 --> 00:49:32.354
And that's going to keep
the creativity here as well.

